      • JSValue

        public JSValue(JSContext ctx,
       java.lang.Object val)
        Creates a new JavaScript value from a Java value. Classes supported are: Boolean, Double, Integer, Long, String, and JSString. Any other object will generate an undefined JavaScript value.
        Parameters:
        ctx - The context in which to create the value
        val - The Java value
